triton stone of new orleans owners acquires triton stone group brand triton stone of new orleans owners acquires triton stone group brand corporate headquarters for leading granite wholesaler and distributor relocating to new orleans news provided by triton stone group feb    et share this article new orleans feb   prnewswire  a leading national wholesaler and distributor of granite and other natural stone products is now louisiana owned today triton stone group of new orleans – owned and operated by the jensen companies – announced the acquisition of triton stone group brand effective immediately moving forward the company will be referred to as triton stone group and its corporate headquarters will relocate to new orleans the announcement was made by katie jensen peralta president of triton stone group following more than a  million investment the newly acquired triton stone group will continue the tradition set forth by triton stone group of new orleans which was established in  by operating as a womenowned business with the two jensen sisters at the helm katie jensen peralta will serve as president and rachel jensen jones will serve as vicepresident   we are so excited about the acquisition and future growth of triton stone group we started triton stone group of new orleans ten years ago and this city has given us so much to be thankful for said peralta as a family company with deep roots in new orleans we remain deeply invested in the future of both our employees and triton stone group triton stone group will relocate its corporate headquarters from southaven ms to an existing new orleans area office located at  river road harahan la  southaven will remain an operating triton stone group location so no workforce changes are anticipated because of the corporate headquarters transfer   furthermore louisiana economic development led committed a  performancebased economic development award program grant to offset part of the cost of a new value added distribution facility triton stone group plans to build on port of new orleans property the new  square foot facility is anticipated to break ground spring  as a result of leds support triton stone group is projecting the creation of  permanent fulltime jobs ranging from corporate positions to managers to dock and warehouse workers this new chapter in the history of triton stone group is a testament to louisianas strong business climate and unrivaled geographic resources gov edwards said this project merges several importing efforts to the port of new orleans providing triton stone group with strengthened logistics capabilities and creating great new job opportunities for our people we congratulate triton stone group on its continued growth this new activity is representative of strong louisianagrown entrepreneurship triton stone group gained five new locations as a result of this acquisition – southaven ms little rock ar knoxville tn huntsville al and birmingham al additionally it owns and operates nine locations across the southeastern united states – new orleans la baton rouge la san antonio tx austin tx mobile al portsmouth va richmond va raleigh nc and charleston sc in total triton stone group employs  employees across  locations in nine states triton stone group also has independently owned and operated licensees in the following seven cities – dallas tx nashville tn atlanta ga fort myers fl port charlotte fl fort lauderdale fl and orlando fl a leading importer and distributor of granite and other natural stone products triton stone group was formed in  and also sells many highquality kitchen and bath products for more information about triton stone group visit wwwtritonstonecom or engage with triton stone group on instagram tritonstonegroup editors note highres images of new triton stone group leadership and its new orleans la distribution center  river road harahan la  are available via dropbox by clicking here   about triton stone group  formed in  triton stone group is a leading importer and distributor of granite and other natural stone products triton stone group provides the highest quality natural stone with a commitment to service and a customersfirst attitude with  locations and seven independently owned and operated licensees across the southeastern united states triton stone group has access to one of the largest stone slab inventories in the united states  to view the original version on pr newswire visithttpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasestritonstoneofneworleansownersacquirestritonstonegroupbrandhtml source triton stone group related links httpwwwtritonstonecom my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen you just read triton stone of new orleans owners acquires triton stone group brand news provided by triton stone group feb    et share this article looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distribution platform sign up to get started request more information have an account log in search searching for your content advanced search triton consolidated inc acquires apple fabrication company contact us member loginregister new account my  press release account media desk for journalists bloggers  readers all press releases for july   » email this story printer friendly pdf version rss feed triton consolidated inc acquires apple fabrication company increasing manufacturing capability and adding new product lines triton consolidated purchases apple fabrication of duncanville tx with the acquisition of apple fabrication triton consolidated expands our capability to manufacture the different parts and assemblies in our product lines    dallas tx july   pressrelease  triton consolidated inc announces the acquisition of apple fabrication company apple fabrication in duncanville texas for nearly twenty years apple fabrication has manufactured and sold high quality polymer and stainless steel tanks vessels and other fabricated products with the acquisition of apple fabrication triton consolidated expands our capability to manufacture the different parts and assemblies in our product lines and bring the manufacturing of steel stainless high density polymers and other materials in house said perry jasin chief executive officer of triton consolidated not only the addition of new product lines but the flexibility to manufacture and incorporate these new capabilities allows for the continuing improvement of our current product lines both in the elevator division and in the ground support equipment division the integration of apple fabrication opens the path to synergize functions and capabilities across the divisions this is an exciting time this increases our manufacturing abilities and allows us to control the quality and delivery of many of our fabricated components said derald armstrong triton consolidated chief operating officer the ability to easily adapt and control the fabrication of parts and assemblies allows for a more rapid response both to opportunities and market needs apple fabrication has been producing high quality industrial steel tanks and vessels since  serving markets throughout north america the company has provided high quality solutions for specialized applications in hazardous high pressure caustic clean room and volatile environments utilizing steel stainless polymer and highly specialized materials apple fabrication products have earned the reputation of being engineered correctly to be right the first time we are happy to join the triton consolidated team to continue delivering a quality product and increase market opportunities jack green the founder of apple fabrication company statedabout triton consolidated inc triton consolidated inc in duncanville texas is the holding company that has recently acquired triton elevator llc and apple fabrication company and is currently in the elevator and aviation ground support equipment business tritons quality products are setting a new standard for reliability and ease of installation  read more press releases from don criswelltriton gse and page industries join forces in global distribution agreementlucas cappelletti accepts director of sales and marketing responsibilities with triton elevators llcgary w phillips accepts president responsibilities with triton applied systems inctriton consolidated announces advisory board appointmenttriton consolidated announces acquisition of manufacturing facility comment on this story share this story contact information don criswelltriton consolidated incdallas texasusavoice email email us herewebsite visit our website like this story i like it  tweets disclaimer if you have any questions regarding information in this press release please contact the person listed in the contact module of this page please do not attempt to contact  press release newswire we are unable to assist you with any information regarding this release  press release newswire disclaims any content contained in this press release please see our complete terms of service disclaimer for more information microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what browser you use open options or settings make sure that thirdparty cookies are not blocked anymore to find out how search your browser’s help revisit httpchoicemicrosoftcomoptout and then on the “personalized ads in this browser” tile click off ext about our ads to create a more customized online experience some of the ads you may receive 