ainable operational improvements and growth the  companies currently in tritons portfolio have combined sales of around € billion and around  employees the triton funds are advised by dedicated teams of professionals based in germany sweden norway finland denmark italy the united kingdom the united states china luxembourg and jersey for further information wwwtritonpartnerscom press contacts triton marcus brans                                                  phone               wernerco marquita kordes phone     ext sign up here to receive email news notifications email pageprint page our locations germany sweden united kingdom jersey china luxembourg united states of america  for legal entities please see the legal notice triton this website is not directed at visitors who are located within the us see legal notice  terms and conditions legal notice cookie policy sitemap copyright triton  view the full site english deutsch basic information dansk español français italiano nederlands norge suomi sverige close triton acquisition holding co company profile  bloomberg feedback triton acquisition holding co private company company profile sector financials industry asset management subindustry investment companies triton acquisition holding co is headquartered in the united states the companys line of business includes investing in commodity contracts tax liens venture capital companies and other miscellaneous investing corporate information address phone  fax  from the web sponsored financial commentaries more from the web home news top headlines most popular exclusive law entrepreneurs leaders economy environment science sports markets magazine pursuits magazine bloomberg visual data bloomberg best and worst for comments or complaints about news coverage click here regions us china europe asia uk  ireland australia  new zealand canada india  pakistan japan africa eastern europe latin america middle east markets commodities currencies bonds stocks energy markets munic